37 namespace Alis.Core.Graphic.SDL
38 {
42  public static class Sdl
43  {
47  static Sdl()
48  {
49  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.OSX))
50  {
51  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
52  {
53  case Architecture.Arm64:
54  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dylib", NativeGraphic.osx_arm64_sdl2);
55  break;
56  case Architecture.X64:
57  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dylib", NativeGraphic.osx_x64_sdl2);
58  break;
59  }
60  }
61 
62  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.Windows))
63  {
64  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
65  {
66  case Architecture.Arm64:
67  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_arm64_sdl2);
68  break;
69  case Architecture.X86:
70  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_x86_sdl2);
71  break;
72  case Architecture.X64:
73  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.dll", NativeGraphic.win_x64_sdl2);
74  break;
75  }
76  }
77 
78  if (RuntimeInformation.IsOSPlatform(OSPlatform.Linux))
79  {
80  switch (RuntimeInformation.ProcessArchitecture)
81  {
82  case Architecture.Arm64:
83  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.so", NativeGraphic.linux_arm64_sdl2);
84  break;
85  case Architecture.X64:
86  EmbeddedDllClass.ExtractEmbeddedDlls("sdl2.so", NativeGraphic.linux_x64_sdl2);
87  break;
88  }
89  }
90  }

95  private const string NativeLibName = "sdl2";

104  internal static int Utf8Size(string str)
105  {
106  if (str == null)
107  {
108  return 0;
109  }
110 
111  return str.Length * 4 + 1;
112  }
113 
121  internal static byte[] Utf8Encode(string str, byte[] buffer, int bufferSize)
122  {
123  if (str == null)
124  {
125  return null;
126  }
127 
128  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
129  buffer[str.Length] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
130 
131  return buffer;
132  }
133 
134 
135 
141  internal static byte[] Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
142  {
143  if (str == null)
144  {
145  return null;
146  }
147 
148  int bufferSize = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(str) + 1;
149  byte[] buffer = new byte[bufferSize];
150  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
151  buffer[bufferSize - 1] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
152 
153  return buffer;
154  }
155 
156 
157 
164  public static string UTF8_ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
165  {
166  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
167  {
168  return null;
169  }
170 
171  byte[] bytes = new byte[0];
172  int len = 0;
173  while (Marshal.ReadByte(s, len) != 0)
174  {
175  len++;
176  }
177 
178  if (len == 0)
179  {
180  return string.Empty;
181  }
182 
183  bytes = new byte[len];
184  Marshal.Copy(s, bytes, 0, len);
185  string result = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(bytes);
186 
187  if (freePtr)
188  {
189  SDL_free(s);
190  }
191 
192  return result;
193  }

205  public static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

333  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_RWFromFile", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
334  private static extern IntPtr INTERNAL_SDL_RWFromFile(
335  byte[] file,
336  byte[] mode
337  );
338 
345  public static IntPtr SDL_RWFromFile(
346  string file,
347  string mode
348  )
349  {
350  byte[] utf8File = Utf8EncodeHeap(file);
351  byte[] utf8Mode = Utf8EncodeHeap(mode);
352  IntPtr rwOps = INTERNAL_SDL_RWFromFile(
353  utf8File,
354  utf8Mode
355  );
356  return rwOps;
357  }

606  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_LoadFile", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
607  private static extern IntPtr INTERNAL_SDL_LoadFile(byte[] file, out IntPtr datasize);
608 
615  public static IntPtr SDL_LoadFile(string file, out IntPtr datasize)
616  {
617  byte[] utf8File = Utf8EncodeHeap(file);
618  IntPtr result = INTERNAL_SDL_LoadFile(utf8File, out datasize);
619  return result;
620  }

2060  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2061  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid);
2062 
2063 
2069  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2070  {
2071  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2072  {
2073  return IntPtr.Zero;
2074  }
2075 
2076  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2077  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
2078  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2079  return mem;
2080  }
2081 
2088  public static int SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid)
2089  {
2090  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2091  {
2092  flags = messageboxdata.flags,
2093  window = messageboxdata.window,
2094  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.title),
2095  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.message),
2096  numbuttons = messageboxdata.numbuttons
2097  };
2098 
2099  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageboxdata.numbuttons];
2100  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2101 
2102  try
2103  {
2104  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
2105  {
2106  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2107  {
2108  flags = messageboxdata.buttons[i].flags,
2109  buttonid = messageboxdata.buttons[i].buttonid,
2110  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.buttons[i].text)
2111  };
2112  }
2113 
2114  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2115  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2116  {
2117  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + (i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2118  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2119  }
2120 
2121  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2122 
2123  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2124  if (messageboxdata.colorScheme != null)
2125  {
2126  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2127  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageboxdata.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2128  }
2129 
2130  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonid);
2131 
2132  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
2133  {
2134  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2135  }
2136 
2137  SDL_free(data.message);
2138  SDL_free(data.title);
2139 
2140  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2141  {
2142  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2143  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2144  }
2145 
2146  return result;
2147  }
2148  finally
2149  {
2150  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2151  {
2152  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2153  }
2154  }
2155  }

5957  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);
5958 
5968  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFORMAT(
5969  SdlPixelType type,
5970  uint order,
5971  SdlPackedLayout layout,
5972  byte bits,
5973  byte bytes
5974  )
5975  => (uint) (
5976  (1 << 28) |
5977  ((byte) type << 24) |
5978  ((byte) order << 20) |
5979  ((byte) layout << 16) |
5980  (bits << 8) |
5981  bytes
5982  );
5983 
5989  public static byte SDL_PIXELFLAG(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
5990 
5996  public static byte SDL_PIXELTYPE(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
5997 
6003  public static byte SDL_PIXELORDER(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
6004 
6010  public static byte SDL_PIXELLAYOUT(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6011 
6017  public static byte SDL_BITSPERPIXEL(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
6018 
6024  public static byte SDL_BYTESPERPIXEL(uint x)
6025  {
6026  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(x))
6027  {
6028  if (x == SdlPixelformatYuy2 ||
6029  x == SdlPixelformatUyvy ||
6030  x == SdlPixelformatYvyu)
6031  {
6032  return 2;
6033  }
6034 
6035  return 1;
6036  }
6037 
6038  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6039  }
6040 
6046  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_INDEXED(uint format)
6047  {
6048  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6049  {
6050  return false;
6051  }
6052 
6053  SdlPixelType pType =
6054  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6055  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6056  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6057  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6058  }
6059 
6065  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(uint format)
6066  {
6067  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6068  {
6069  return false;
6070  }
6071 
6072  SdlPixelType pType =
6073  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6074  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6075  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6076  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6077  }
6078 
6084  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(uint format)
6085  {
6086  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6087  {
6088  return false;
6089  }
6090 
6091  SdlPixelType pType =
6092  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6093  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6094  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6095  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6096  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6097  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6098  }
6099 
6105  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ALPHA(uint format)
6106  {
6107  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(format))
6108  {
6109  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6110  (SdlPackedOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6111  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6112  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6113  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6114  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6115  }
6116 
6117  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(format))
6118  {
6119  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6120  (SdlArrayOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6121  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6122  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6123  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6124  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6125  }
6126 
6127  return false;
6128  }
6129

7914 
7921  public static SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7922  out SdlEventFilter filter,
7923  out IntPtr userdata
7924  )
7925  {
7926  IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;
7927  SdlBool retval = SDL_GetEventFilter(out result, out userdata);
7928  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
7929  {
7930  filter = (SdlEventFilter) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
7931  result,
7932  typeof(SdlEventFilter)
7933  );
7934  }
7935  else
7936  {
7937  filter = null;
7938  }
7939 
7940  return retval;
7941  }

9534  public static SdlGameControllerButtonBind SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9535  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9536  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9537  )
9538  {
9539  // This is guaranteed to never be null
9540  InternalSdlGameControllerButtonBind dumb = INTERNAL_SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9541  gamecontroller,
9542  axis
9543  );
9544  SdlGameControllerButtonBind result = new SdlGameControllerButtonBind();
9545  result.bindType = (SdlGameControllerBindType) dumb.bindType;
9546  result.value.hat.hat = dumb.unionVal0;
9547  result.value.hat.hat_mask = dumb.unionVal1;
9548  return result;
